reviews.text: Higher quality Cantonese fast food and with better service than any other chain. This outlet is a bit hidden, which means the dining hall is actually relatively quiet. The same soul food Cantonese dishes as are available at most other places, but with less of the grease and guilt to go with them.

We used to look forward to eating here every time we came to Hong Kong.. This place is a mere shadow of its former self. I don't know what they did to it, but it's not good at all. The service is terrible and the food is almost trash. Avoid this place. Only massive disappointment awaits you here.

reviews.text: 今日食下午茶,太興集團茶餐廳, 真係可以列入黑名單,炒河,炆米可以隔濾到半碗油, 全碟根本多油多到食唔到,中年及老年人千萬要拒絕呢種集團粗制濫做既生意手法,  我唔打算比機會佢地,因為要佢地嚴正跟進,只有拒絕幫襯至最為有效,真心嬲, 因為浪費辛苦賺來既金錢兼會損人健康架, !!
係中學年代已幫襯太安樓太興，奇怪係該集團好似認許實行個別分店風格，例如北角店去咗多次食早餐，有款礼肉湯米，差不多早同晏（十點前）都係話賣晒！好奇怪？
北角七姊妹道健威坊地下，地方不算大但也算清潔。近日推出茶香雞，如在免費報紙剪下coupon,外賣只$68一隻。每天下午四時發售，但因人多購買，建議十五分鐘前要到排隊，否則可能買不到。
員工很有禮。燒味不錯，但其他選擇則不多。
食物質素高 ，好好味 ，瑞士汁牛柳炒濕河啲牛柳係食得嘅👍👍 冰鎮奶茶一樣咁好味👍👍 服務員友善👍👍 環境衛生乾淨

reviews.text: Free 3 hours parking required of $500 consumed by Alipay! It is no longer a good place for parking!
Very good for electronic marchine.
a very convenience shopping mall with all needs for daily life, various kind of restaurant s, supermarket and grocery shops.
You can find some good shops and a few reasonable restaurants in Fitfort.

For car parking, it provides good condition of car parking environment.  They provide day parking until midnight and also provided max. 3 hrs free parking for only HK$200 spending in plaza.  Hence it seems to be the lowest price day parking available in North Point. (Last updated on 31/12/2017)
